{"tid":1519132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真 如果聽日會死人 你出唔出？","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:18:17.000Z","uid":68084,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6eea208c8b74239ad50588e5a0242719e57e6884","tid":1519132,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日我一撚定出街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府夠膽咪用緊急法囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大把人想全部人一齊死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等左呢刻好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 咩都無既窮人 想香港亂好耐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直都覺得如果無無聊聊咁番工草錢買樓既香港人人生好悶<br />\n<br />\n終於有野玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地焦土派絕對支持香港變成敘利亞🤪🤪🤪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好悶啊 快d打仗啦"},{"pid":"8169333400d14fe35752dc10cf542d54fced7b3e","tid":1519132,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=86c81e48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海<